{"tid":1851080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"柴灣警宿男警一家三口送院 內地親友曾到其家中拜年","createTime":"2020-01-30T01:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T02:54:32.000Z","uid":174649,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0bb4a85fe22cb630288adbeffae72dc4cb5159","tid":1851080,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情來勢洶洶，市民人心惶惶，其中網絡流傳圖片，指今日凌晨多名全副防護裝備醫護人員，到柴灣已婚警察宿舍協助帶走3人上救護車，引起當區居民憂慮。警方晚上證實，事件與一名居住在上址宿舍，隸屬西區警區的男警務人員有關。雖該名男警員自己未有現病徵，但其兩名家屬則有發燒，因此3人現於醫院接受治療及等候測試結果。警方已根據相關指引，於宿舍進行徹底清潔和消毒，亦已提醒警員注意個人衛生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200129/Y36MKD6KNGSNTRNYDYPVXNBM2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200129%2FY36MKD6KNGSNTRNYDYPVXNBM2Q%2F&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=e4150adb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200129%2FY36MKD6KNGSNTRNYDYPVXNBM2Q%2F&h=068e7871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200129/Y36MKD6KNGSNTRNYDYPVXNBM2Q/</a>"},{"pid":"a08b880d5c5d5318b67bcba352ff2e6ce3d8be1b","tid":1851080,"uid":60434,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:30:30.000Z","msg":"快啲確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d413ee099e4c78e77e87e7de8cabd9d7ea5ec4b","tid":1851080,"uid":42090,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200b8910f90bbbdaba21cacb6ba92fd45131bf1e","tid":1851080,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:31:23.000Z","msg":"講真就算戴左口罩同眼鏡都仲有機會中招....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848960</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa8edffdafa9747a94f0d8b4ee7dcfb2e67c45cf","tid":1851080,"uid":29093,"like":